## Description {#details}

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/scheduledagsdnodes/regdefiter">RegDefIter</a> - In place iteration over the values defined by an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/sunit">SUnit</a>.

This does not need copies of the iterator or any other STLisms. The iterator creates itself, rather than being provided by the SchedDAG.

Definition at line 138 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/codegen/lib/codegen/selectiondag/scheduledagsdnodes-h">ScheduleDAGSDNodes.h</a>.
